        {
            "title": "博通確認將向Anthropic供應谷歌TPU晶片 提供輝達技術的替代方案",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 人工智能(AI)公司<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Anthropic\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Anthropic;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Anthropic\">Anthropic</a>表示，其年化收入已超過300億美元，較2025年末的90億美元大幅成長，並證實將與博通和谷歌合作擴大AI算力，為其迅速擴張的業務提供支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic表示，今年以來對其Claude服務的需求加速成長，超過1000家企業客戶在該服務上的年化支出超過100萬美元。這一數字自2月以來已經翻了一倍多。年化收入是科技初創公司常用的一項指標，用於將當前銷售折算為全年規模。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-408bc4a9-d2f8-3fe6-ba5c-411437b981c7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic財務長Krishna Rao在聲明中表示，與博通和谷歌的合作將幫助公司建立足以支撐客戶群驚人成長所需的算力。這一合作在上月首次公佈。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最新數據表明，Anthropic與美國政府之間一場備受關注的爭端並未遏制其成長。此前，在雙方圍繞人工智能安全護欄問題發生爭議後，美國國防部宣布Anthropic對供應鏈構成威脅，公司正就此展開法律訴訟。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">博通確認，將使用谷歌的張量處理單元(TPU)向Anthropic交付晶片，為市場提供了輝達技術的替代方案。三家公司還擴大一項戰略合作，Anthropic將由此獲得約3.5吉瓦的算力。這一安排將從2027年開始。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「Anthropic對上述擴展AI算力的使用取決於其持續的商業成功。圍繞這一部署，各方正與特定的運營及金融合作夥伴進行討論，」博通表示。博通股價在盤後交易中一度上漲3.6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Anthropic Tops $30 Billion Run Rate, Seals Deal With Broadcom</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%9A%E9%80%9A%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E5%B0%87%E5%90%91anthropic%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8Ctpu%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87-%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E8%BC%9D%E9%81%94%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88-221709511.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-07 08:17:43",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "三星電子季度利潤飆升近八倍 人工智能晶片銷售火爆",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 三星電子季度利潤實現超出預期的近八倍成長，凸顯了用於人工智能AI和數據中心的內存晶片需求強勁，儘管中東戰爭引發了不確定性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家業務涵蓋晶片到智慧手機的綜合企業公佈，3月季度的初步營業利潤為57.2萬億韓元（379億美元），這創歷史新高，亦高於分析師平均預期的39.3萬億韓元。當季營收攀升至133萬億韓元，高於分析師平均預期的116.8萬億。該公司將於本月晚些時候發布完整財務報表，其中包括淨利潤和各部門的詳細數據。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8060d562-7e4e-3df7-b3d6-7a7513af8bde-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三星電子股價去年上漲超過120%，但自2月達到峰值以來已下跌約12%，因為人們擔心伊朗衝突可能會引發物價和利率上漲，並損害AI硬體大舉支出勢頭的可持續性。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以雲服務提供商為首的客戶向三星發出大筆訂單，提升了銷量和利潤率。花旗集團分析師Peter Lee和Jayden Oh在4月2日的報告中寫道，全球DRAM平均售價在第一季度較上一季度飆升了64%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">業績公佈之後，三星電子股價在盤前交易中上漲5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">*SAMSUNG JUMPS 5% IN PRE-MARKET TRADING AFTER 1Q EARNINGS</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Samsung Profit Up Eight-Fold After AI Chip Sales Defy War Fears</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Ville Heiskanen.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E5%88%A9%E6%BD%A4%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87%E8%BF%91%E5%85%AB%E5%80%8D-%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E7%81%AB%E7%88%86-232642796.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-07 08:17:45",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "〈能源盤後〉美伊言詞交鋒 川普再威脅炸毀橋樑和電廠 油價攀高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mQUBPpTeX2g9QxblOSp0bA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/f61cb7ac8276b1f526af952fa1ef190f\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E7%9B%A4%E5%BE%8C-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E8%A8%80%E8%A9%9E%E4%BA%A4%E9%8B%92-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%86%8D%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E7%82%B8%E6%AF%80%E6%A9%8B%E6%A8%91%E5%92%8C%E9%9B%BB%E5%BB%A0-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E6%94%80%E9%AB%98-230900262.html",
